---
title: Rustic Fennel and Goat Cheese Tart with Walnut and Fig Green Beans
description: Light and flaky puff pastry is a game-changer when it comes to impressive weeknight meals. You'll love the crunch of the buttery base that's baked to perfection. We've used it to make a tasty onion and goat cheese tart, and served it with sweet figgy green beans.
